{"tid":327690,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本遺失物品求救","createTime":"2017-07-19T03:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T19:30:33.000Z","uid":92162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17803575f29a075f0d5f5b558ae434a8e7af96ce","tid":327690,"uid":92162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲知喺西日本jr唔見咗野點算？<br />\n<br />\n話說尋日16:29由京都去三宮架新快速途中放咗兩袋野上行李架但係落車唔記得拎，<br />\n知唔見野時已經即時仆返去三宮jr車站問站員，點知佢地話無。我而家仲有咩途徑可以搵得返？"},{"pid":"d989dfde2f79d38bf377af5852d2d01fa3608cab","tid":327690,"uid":12827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"當時架車未到尾站無人會發現你件失物吧<br />\n<br />\n聯絡尾站睇下有無啦"},{"pid":"7d105b1e901bc2ee285581a859b3843ae5422a92","tid":327690,"uid":92162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當時架車未到尾站無人會發現你件失物吧<br />\n<br />\n聯絡尾站睇下有無啦</blockquote><br />\n個站員俾咗張紙仔我聯絡西日本客服中心 ，夜晚打去佢都係話無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d53df52cff9f67c681e2a5c12e0f138b0e3b934","tid":327690,"uid":46018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:24:11.000Z","msg":"尾站應該有失物認領處<br />\n之前響九州試過拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f745f7304427ebbdf389fdf1562d8351ddef3f15","tid":327690,"uid":19949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"去姫路搵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ceca8a08c1d49dfa9cca36f7cd6da69d10b8217","tid":327690,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"冇架啦<br />\n上次京都餐廳漏左對鞋<br />\n返住頭問店員都話冇啦"},{"pid":"93682f65a5ca687b93d9abc3c068f8c3e9c535f7","tid":327690,"uid":44509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"我京都去奈良掛住幫條女推行李 ，自己成個背包留左係火車度都搵得番"},{"pid":"afbba8757c1f0a46209f62fb6ee2753711e3f281","tid":327690,"uid":44509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"你去月台搵職員，話留左野係車<br />\n講番幾點咩站上車，幾點咩站落車，唔見D咩<br />\n你慢慢等佢幫你搵<br />\n佢正路會將失物集埋係同一個站。所以未必咁快搵到"},{"pid":"6ada27f4aec2d2fbe1ed9ab5793fd29bf4b03bea","tid":327690,"uid":92162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺姬路搵返喇 多謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d0815982f3dee478b72764ec3f9bcf8afa5647","tid":327690,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱喺姬路搵返喇 多謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n向日本唔見野而又搵得返既機會真係好大，年頭女友向下北澤月台跌左個手袋最後比人執左交比票務部，失而復得既感覺真係好奇妙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04627e63e85e632176e6c7216a9fe97bbdbc4243","tid":327690,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"日本果然係文明之國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1043a97da3c4f1114044a33fbbc614285289342c","tid":327690,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T19:29:35.000Z","msg":"我個親戚漏左個銀包起餐廳reception，兩個鐘先發現，3個鐘返到間餐廳都仲起度。"},{"pid":"c3d27e2c9bd83a4637199837c760f046a47939e7","tid":327690,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T19:30:33.000Z","msg":"你就好<br />\n我上左機<br />\n點拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}